Text:
Joining in the praise!
bitstreeem for teh win!
Bitstreem you guys are just amazingly awesome, seeing these films again brings back such cool childhood memories! I bow down to you in homage!

Not just a Mantis, as the large print declares, but, almost as an after thought, THE DEADLY Mantis. Suddenly we are drawn to it being deadly, not a mere Mantis...but one that kills, or so it is said! Eek!
